title: 820-00875 not turning one.
message:
The board was water damage in U8400 area. So checked all rails and found that PP3V3_S5 is shorted to ground. Checked all components on that line and all seems be ok. Injecting 3V only CPU points where arrives PP3V3_S5  is getting hot. 


CPU is dead or there is something else i can check?
